HEADWORD: Antecedently
<hw>An`te*ced"ent*ly</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<def>Previously; before in time; at a time preceding; <as>as,
<ex>antecedently</ex> to conversion</as>.</def>
